{"tid":1435094,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"推爆元朗狗僭建","createTime":"2019-08-09T03:01:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T05:38:12.000Z","uid":298077,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"65b7343fb27ba91c61a44816ec04f292b71b5ffa","tid":1435094,"uid":298077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:01:19.000Z","msg":"《蘋果》調查發現，洪水橋一幅鄧氏原居民持有的祖堂地，近年非法僭建一個逾1.5萬方呎的大型金屬構建物，用作汽車維修及存放鋼筋，內裡更設數幢兩層高「貨櫃屋」。涉事祖堂地的代表司理，正是元朗恐襲事件中被捕的江湖人物鄧志學。<br />\n#蘋果踢爆<br />\n【7.21白衣猛人「鬥雞學」 元朗祖堂地涉僭建兩層高貨櫃屋】<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2YUYDFk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2YUYDFk&d=OHH5ZFb8IkVcKCzgNN0rzV3VpWtqcNNCzs9YdIyDBYU%3D&h=15197d88\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2YUYDFk</a>"},{"pid":"aa17fad113b0d90b8b2078ca1e55b646cdc12f35","tid":1435094,"uid":171874,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T03:01:56.000Z","msg":"//現加嘅情況同雨傘後期有啲相似<br />\n大家開始放低咗個戒心<br />\n照樣將專意力去恥笑黑警er.er.er記者會<br />\n左膠、分化慢慢抬頭//"},{"pid":"44dd9521cc87be2986b2812e0ba4d21bf43540e6","tid":1435094,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:25:30.000Z","msg":"推！點投訴"},{"pid":"ebd3168cdc03d966e260f8ac2649a2cae77ec44f","tid":1435094,"uid":298077,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"44dd9521cc87be2986b2812e0ba4d21bf43540e6","tid":1435094,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:25:30.000Z","msg":"推！點投訴"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:35:22.000Z","msg":"寫信?<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61ff504763de1c349476566504a5f810f2b52a9","tid":1435094,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ebd3168cdc03d966e260f8ac2649a2cae77ec44f","tid":1435094,"uid":298077,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"44dd9521cc87be2986b2812e0ba4d21bf43540e6","tid":1435094,"uid":55010,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T05:25:30.000Z","msg":"推！點投訴"},